HEADWORD: Micher
<hw>Mich"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>michare</ets>, <ets>muchare</ets>. See <er>Mich</er>.]</ety>
<def>One who skulks, or keeps out of sight; hence, a truant; an idler; a
thief, etc.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
